# AI Token Calculator - Environment Variables Template
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values

# Note: This is a static site that runs entirely in the browser.
# No API keys are currently needed for the core functionality.

# If you plan to add API integration in the future:
# VITE_OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_key_here
# VITE_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_anthropic_key_here
# VITE_GOOGLE_API_KEY=your_google_key_here

